channel.title: Anyone want any help with a server? :-)
channel.description:
[center]I am looking for someone who has just started a 'RSPS' and would like help with it.. I would prefere it if it was already online and active, and if you give me co-ownership (player rights 3) i could help you become big! :-)
Well i am an experienced java coder :-) i know how to keep a good economy, basically how to keep your server alive :-) I could almost do anything in java coding, i am full of idea's for keeping the server better..
I say with my help, within the first week you could have 50+ players on at a time (preferably if your server is 24/7)..
Comment or send me a mail :-) Hope to hear from you soon.
[u]OR[/u].. Does anyone want any help overall? :-) i will do a tutorial for whatever you need/want? Or show you how to do it.. :-)
Many thanks, Lee [/center]
